This Privacy Policy describes how your personal information is collected, used, and shared when you use the Python Quiz mobile application (the “App”) developed by Danijel Pavlek.

Personal Information We Collect

When you use the App, we may collect certain information about you, including:

Device Information: We may collect information about the mobile device you use to access the App, including the device type, operating system, and unique device identifier.

Usage Information: We may collect information about how you use the App, including the quizzes you take, the questions you answer correctly or incorrectly, and your score.

Purchase Information: If you make a one-time purchase within the App, we may collect information about your transaction, such as your name, billing address, and payment information.

Advertising Data: We may collect data about the ads displayed in the App, including the type of ad, the advertiser, and the number of times an ad is displayed.

Local Storage: We may collect data that you store locally on your device, such as your quiz history or preferences.

How We Use Your Personal Information

We use the personal information we collect to:

Provide and maintain the App;

Improve the App and our services;

Analyze how the App is used and identify areas for improvement;

Personalize your experience with the App;

Process and fulfill your one-time purchases;

Display advertising that is relevant to you based on your interests;

Detect and prevent fraud and other illegal activities.

How We Share Your Personal Information

We may share your personal information with third parties in the following circumstances:

With our service providers: We may share your personal information with third-party service providers that assist us in operating the App and providing our services. These service providers may include payment processors, analytics providers, and advertising partners.

With advertisers: We may share non-personally identifiable information about you with advertisers in order to display targeted advertising in the App.

With legal authorities: We may share your personal information if we are required to do so by law or if we believe that such action is necessary to comply with a legal obligation or to protect and defend our rights and property.

Your Choices

You can choose to disable the collection of certain data by adjusting the settings on your device or within the App. However, please note that disabling certain data collection may impact your experience with the App.

You may also opt-out of targeted advertising by adjusting the settings on your device or within the App.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time in order to reflect changes to our data practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at danijel.pavlek777@gmail.com.
